name: Ace
cardText: Complete a contract with 2 or more Hazard Dice targeting you.

name: Barrage
cardText: Play at least 5 Damage on the same contract.

name: Chain Reaction
cardText: Play at least 4 Reactor cards on the same contract.

name: Daredevil
cardText: Play no Shield cards but complete a Rescue contract.

name: Efficiency
cardText: Play no Thruster cards but complete a Delivery contract.

name: Fire Support
cardText: Play no Damage cards, but complete a Kill contract.

name: Generalist
cardText: Have a Magnomi, Henko, Komek, and Ventus ship part attached to your ship.

name: Gun For Hire
cardText: Complete a Kill contract alone.

name: Megaton
cardText: Acquire 3 Magnomi ship parts for your ship.

name: Money Bags
cardText: Have 8 Credits at the end of your turn.

name: Natural Leader
cardText: Play at least 3 Crew Members on the same contract.

name: Over 9000
cardText: Acquire 3 Komek ship parts for your ship.

name: Quick Run
cardText: Complete a Delivery contract alone.

name: Quick Strike
cardText: Play at least 3 Thruster cards on the same contract.

name: Saboteur
cardText: Fail a contract as an ally.

name: Santa Maria
cardText: Complete an Explore contract alone.

name: Shield Wall
cardText: Play at least 3 Shield cards on the same contract.

name: Specialist
cardText: Acquire 2 Sorelia ship parts for your ship.

name: Speed Demon
cardText: Acquire 3 Ventus ship parts for your ship.

name: Tank
cardText: Acquire 3 Henko ship parts for your ship.

name: Tinker
cardText: After acquiring 4 ship parts, replace a part on your ship.

name: Utopia
cardText: Complete a contract with all other players as allies.

name: You're My Hero
cardText: Complete a Rescue contract alone.

name: Alliance
cardText: Have 5 Faction Rep with one faction and 0 with all others.

name: Backup
cardText: Gain 4 Faction Rep on the same contract.

name: Brute
cardText: Fail a contract as an ally with the player in first or tied for first.

name: Call in Favors
cardText: Spend 10 Faction Rep on the same turn.

name: For Hire
cardText: Spend Faction Rep to get 2 objectives in the same turn.

name: Freeloader
cardText: Join a contract for no reward.

name: Hoarder
cardText: Have a total of 20 cards between your hand, draw pile, and discard pile.

name: Invest
cardText: Spend Faction Rep to gain at least 3 Credits in the same turn.

name: Manifold
cardText: Gain 3 Cards on the same contract using Faction Rep.

name: Responsive
cardText: Gain 3 Actions on the same contract using Faction Rep.

name: Arsenal
cardText: Play 3 different types of Damage cards on the same turn.

name: Tactical
cardText: Play at least 2 Shield cards and 2 Damage cards on the same contract.

name: IO-Adopter
cardText: Have two cards with at least 1 [IO-Sphere] on them.

name: IO-Hoard
cardText: Have a total of 6 [IO-Sphere] on your cards.

name: IO-Power
cardText: Remove 3 [IO-Sphere] on the same turn.

name: Junker
cardText: Trash at least 2 cards on the same turn.

name: Parasite
cardText: Complete a contract without playing any cards.

name: Technologic
cardText: Play 3 different types of Advanced action cards on the same turn.

name: Untouchable
cardText: Block 2 Hazard without playing a Shield on the same contract.

name: Weird Flex
cardText: Complete a contract with Flex requirements alone.

name: Advantageous
cardText: Trash a card during an Event.

name: Clandestine
cardText: Complete a Contract on Sorelia with no allies.

name: Harmony
cardText: All players vote unanimously on a Policy.

name: Opulence
cardText: Gain 2 Sorelia Protype Ship Parts.

name: Benefactor
cardText: Take all Hazard Dice and no Credits on a contract.

name: Blessing
cardText: Roll 2 blanks while rolling Hazard Dice.

name: Glare of Space
cardText: Roll 2 matching dice on your turn.

name: Ms. Fortune
cardText: Gain a Bonus Card worth less than 4 Credits.

name: Royale
cardText: Gain a Bonus Card worth more than 3 Credits.
